'''VRChat France''' is a French-speaking community on [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]], established in 2020. It aims to unite French speakers to share and create events, exchange information, and support both new and experienced players within the VRChat platform.

==Website==
The [https://vrchatfrance.fr/ VRChat France Website] serves as a resource hub for the French-speaking VRChat community, providing information and tools to enhance user experiences. The site includes several sections that cater to the community's needs.

==VRChat's Docs translation==
The VRChat France team has translated the official VRChat documents into French, providing French speakers with a resource for better understanding the official VRChat documentation, but since the arrival of the [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Page|VRChat Wiki]] it now redirects to its home page.

